# [SCOPE] - [User-facing description]
#
# Commit messages become PR titles, GitHub release changelog entries,
# in-app news feed entries, and Discord release text.
#
# Write for players:
# - Describe what changed, not how it was implemented.
# - Avoid file names, code references, IDs, and internal implementation details.
# - Do not include agent/tool attribution such as codex, claude, generated by,
#   co-authored-by, openai, anthropic, ai, or agent unless explicitly requested.
#
# Common scopes:
# GNB, MCH, WHM, DRK, PLD, WAR, SCH, SGE, AST, BRD, DNC, NIN, SAM, MNK, DRG,
# RPR, VPR, BLM, SMN, RDM, PCT, BLU
# TANKS, HEALERS, MELEE, RANGED, ALL, PVP, Core, FightLogic, Magitek
#
# Examples:
# GNB - Fix low level Optimized Burst rotation down to level 60
# FightLogic - Add all bosses for Windurst: The Third Walk
# MCH - Add experimental options for guaranteed 6GCD wildfires
